{"tid":1534622,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"<搜證> 太子血跡","createTime":"2019-09-03T05:17:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-06T13:06:18.000Z","uid":297736,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"33df284a573d5c7f24dbf015873793b2340a29c0","tid":1534622,"uid":297736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:17:59.000Z","msg":"唔講咁多去圖先<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/anteaD1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FanteaD1.png&h=3f17ea20&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3aqoOqO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3aqoOqO.png&h=28e62aed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n岩岩去太子現場睇過 基本上所有證據都冇哂<br />\n但係係牆到搵到懷疑血跡 係紅線往中環方向<br />\n7-4車廂果到 最近嘅以家CCTV亦都向住反方向<br />\n究竟入面發生左乜撚野事？ 清咁耐都仲有血跡<br />\nCCTV DLLM<br />\n追究恐襲"},{"pid":"d3a83311e2f0e0787c7da42ec68168c06c107948","tid":1534622,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:18:16.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1c3006345cb314ac662bfe1958a16d798e77d044","tid":1534622,"uid":11698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:24:48.000Z","msg":"屌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61b234a8aabd0d243265b0aba31e03da575d736d","tid":1534622,"uid":282490,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:27:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2781ed2d2d8eb545eae273277a21a8f76338f6a6","tid":1534622,"uid":289649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:39:12.000Z","msg":"明白大家呢排嘅士氣經過<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">831恐襲</span></span>同<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">901大撤退</span></span>之後好低落<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我同大家一樣都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但越係呢啲時候<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我地就越要堅持下去，<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">團結一致</span></span><br />\n唔好比林鄭見我地冇士氣而去捉多啲人<br />\n<br />\n以下兩篇文章<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">無論<span style=\"color: gold;\">和理非</span>，定係<span style=\"color: red;\">勇武</span>，都應該入黎，打返枝<span style=\"color: violet;\">強心針</span></span><br />\n<br />\n希望可以幫到大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n記得share比身邊因近日事件而唔開心嘅朋友仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n［全部人同我入黎］《致眾表》望各位香港市民出自己的一份綿力<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1532967\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1532967</a><br />\n<br />\n灰心喪志，是因為你看不見抗爭的前路<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1533741\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1533741</a>"},{"pid":"7c4a4c6ec64c3471894826ec826c5660124fa6af","tid":1534622,"uid":158613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:51:03.000Z","msg":"push!!"},{"pid":"8df036e28d269586c5c2769650d173858d3d595f","tid":1534622,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:52:18.000Z","msg":"可能被支解左"},{"pid":"822ce7901a4ce400de022fe3ba7a69e9d29c971e","tid":1534622,"uid":123111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:53:24.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58b4a1703357703ad049ac2459f97861bb0bc837","tid":1534622,"uid":268541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:08:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"62a3e1fae58820eca8e669c2073e2211afa0d327","tid":1534622,"uid":124180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:46:06.000Z","msg":"太子站開番?"},{"pid":"5c83578967cd91d780786638067e5674bb676eff","tid":1534622,"uid":23587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:59:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0f0375bc15906ec0b8d1efdfddbc76c096b6fc9","tid":1534622,"uid":265179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T07:01:27.000Z","msg":"攞DNA得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/w